{
  "stem": "1753.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We figured maybe 70% to 80% of us would die, but some of us would survive, no chance, because of a mass uprising no way that someone could not survive.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We had our orders towards a careful plan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We went to bed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Some of us were involved to a limited extent, like myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I didn't know that much about-- they just told me what to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was a higher up group of the prisoners that was-- were more intelligent.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They know what to do, and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They gave us their orders.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to our bunks and laid down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] About 11:00, 12:00 in the evening, the Nazis come in, one, this Untersturmfuhrer Lantz, who I testified in Vienna in the war crimes trials.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I testified in five, by the way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That I subsequently in 1962, I was at his trial in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He came in, looked around, didn't ask-- check if people are dressed or not.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When he left, a few minutes later, we were told we have to forget this uprising, because we understand they're aware when our plans was.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this electrical engineer that built-- Rikno-- that built that locomobile, which creates the-- the turbine for the generator, for the light generators, he was a trustee of the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had a wife and two children there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He told them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that annihilated-- that-- that did away with our plans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He went to the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's a known fact.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So life went on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The guns came closer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the 23rd of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] July, 1944, it was a Sunday.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a dispute whether it was the 23rd or was the 25th, or what it was.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
